Additional information about migrations and db creations 
Initialize prisma
npx prisma init --datasource-provider postgresql

configure db url for schema file

create model

Migrate db
npx prisma migrate dev --name init

docker container start from db docker file
docker compose up -d

Drizzle for OM Service
DB Migrations 

Run Package.json scripts step by step
db:generate
db:migrate
